Phn tch d liu li sng nhm h tr ra quyt nh ci thin sc khe

Phn loi (Classification): "Yu t li sng v sc khe no (Stress Level, Sleep Duration, BMI, etc.) l quan trng nht trong vic d on mt ngi c b ri lon gic ng (Sleep Disorder) hay khng?"

Phn cm (Clustering): "Liu c th phn chia cc c nhn thnh cc nhm (Persona) vi cc c im li sng v ri ro sc khe khc nhau, v c im ca mi nhm l g?"

In[1144]:
def group_occupation(job):
    if job in ['Nurse', 'Doctor']:
        return 'Healthcare'
    elif job in ['Engineer', 'Lawyer', 'Accountant', 'Software Engineer', 'Manager']:
        return 'Professional_Office'
    elif job in ['Salesperson', 'Sales Representative']:
        return 'Sales'
    elif job in ['Teacher', 'Scientist']:
        return 'Academic_Science'
    else:
        return 'Other'

df['Occupation_Group'] = df['Occupation'].apply(group_occupation)

df['Occupation_Group'].value_counts()

# Biu  2: Heatmap th hin "Vng cht lng"
# Gom nhm  tnh cht lng gic ng trung bnh cho mi cp Stress-Thi lng ng
pivot_table = df.pivot_table(index='Stress Level',
                             columns=pd.cut(df['Sleep Duration'], bins=4),
                             values='Quality of Sleep',
                             aggfunc='mean')

plt.subplot(1, 2, 2)
sns.heatmap(pivot_table, annot=True, cmap='RdYlGn', cbar_kws={'label': 'Cht lng ng (1-10)'})
plt.title('Ma trn "Vng Ng Ngon": Stress vs Thi lng ng', fontsize=13)

import pandas as pd
from mlxtend.frequent_patterns import apriori, association_rules
# Chun b d liu cho quy lut
df_rules = df.copy()

# Chia Huyt p tm thu (Systolic BP) thnh nhm
df_rules['Systolic_Group'] = pd.cut(df['Systolic BP'], bins=[0, 120, 135, 200], labels=['Normal_BP', 'Elevated_BP', 'High_BP'])

# Chia Stress Level thnh nhm
df_rules['Stress_Group'] = pd.cut(df['Stress Level'], bins=[0, 4, 7, 10], labels=['Low_Stress', 'Mid_Stress', 'High_Stress'])

# Chia Tui thnh nhm
df_rules['Age_Group'] = pd.cut(df['Age'], bins=[0, 35, 50, 100], labels=['Young', 'Middle_Aged', 'Senior'])

columns_for_rules = ['Gender', 'Occupation_Group', 'BMI Category', 'Sleep Disorder',
                     'Systolic_Group', 'Stress_Group', 'Age_Group']

# Chuyn i sang One-Hot Encoding
df_onehot = pd.get_dummies(df_rules[columns_for_rules], columns=columns_for_rules)

frequent_itemsets = apriori(df_onehot, min_support=0.1, use_colnames=True)

rules = association_rules(frequent_itemsets, metric="lift", min_threshold=1.2)

sleep_rules = rules[rules['consequents'].astype(str).str.contains('Sleep Disorder_')]

display(sleep_rules[['antecedents', 'consequents', 'support', 'confidence', 'lift']].sort_values(by='confidence', ascending=False).head(10))

INSIGHT THEO CU HI NGHIN CU

1. Insight cho bi ton Phn loi (Classification)

Cu hi:

  • Yu t li sng v sc khe no l quan trng nht trong vic d on mt ngi c b ri lon gic ng (Sleep Disorder) hay khng?

Insight chnh

Kt qu m hnh phn loi cho thy Stress Level l yu t d bo quan trng nht i vi kh nng mc ri lon gic ng, vt tri so vi cc bin cn li nh Sleep Duration hay Physical Activity Level.

Phn tch insight

  • Stress Level c mc nh hng cao nht:

    • Khi Stress tng, xc sut xut hin Sleep Disorder (Insomnia, Sleep Apnea) tng r rt.

    • Stress khng ch tc ng trc tip n gic ng m cn lm suy gim kh nng phc hi ca c th.

  • BMI Category l yu t quan trng th hai:

    • Nhm Overweight/Obese c nguy c mc ri lon gic ng cao hn ng k so vi nhm BMI Normal.

    • iu ny c bit r rng i vi Sleep Apnea.

  • Sleep Duration c nh hng nhng khng mang tnh quyt nh:

    • Ng t gi lm tng nguy c ri lon gic ng, tuy nhin nu Stress thp th nguy c vn c kim sot.

  • Physical Activity Level ng vai tr bo v gin tip:

    • Mc vn ng cao gip gim Stress, t lm gim kh nng mc Sleep Disorder.

Insight tng hp (Classification)

Ri lon gic ng khng n thun l h qu ca vic thiu ng, m ch yu xut pht t cng thng ko di kt hp vi tnh trng th cht km (BMI cao).

2. Insight cho bi ton Phn cm (Clustering)

Cu hi:

  • Liu c th phn chia cc c nhn thnh cc nhm (Persona) vi c im li sng v ri ro sc khe khc nhau hay khng, v c im ca mi nhm l g?

Insight chnh

  • Phn tch phn cm cho thy c th chia c nhn thnh cc nhm (persona) r rt, mi nhm i din cho mt kiu li sng v mc ri ro ri lon gic ng khc nhau.

Cc nhm Persona tiu biu

Nhm 1: Persona Khe mnh Nguy c thp

  • Stress Level: Thp

  • Physical Activity Level: Cao

  • BMI: Normal

  • Sleep Duration & Quality: n nh

  • Sleep Disorder: Hu nh khng c

Insight: y l nhm c li sng lnh mnh, Stress c kim sot tt nn nguy c ri lon gic ng gn nh khng ng k.

Nhm 2: Persona Ng nhng Stress cao

  • Stress Level: Trung bnh Cao

  • Sleep Duration: Thp hoc Trung Bnh

  • Physical Activity Level: Trung bnh

  • Sleep Disorder: Ch yu l Insomnia

Insight: Ng gi khng m bo trnh c ri lon gic ng nu Stress khng c kim sot. y l nhm d b mt ng do p lc tinh thn.

Nhm 3: Persona Nguy c cao Li sng km lnh mnh

  • Stress Level: Cao

  • Physical Activity Level: Thp

  • BMI: Overweight/Obese

  • Sleep Duration: Thp hoc khng n nh

  • Sleep Disorder: T l cao (c bit Sleep Apnea)

Insight: S kt hp gia Stress cao, t vn ng v BMI cao to ra nguy c ri lon gic ng nghim trng nht.

  • D hot ng th cht cao (nh Y t), nhng do c th cng vic p lc v ch s BMI cao (Overweight), nhm ny vn c t l Sleep Apnea cao nht.

Insight tng hp (Clustering)

Cc c nhn khng ging nhau v ri ro gic ng; ri lon gic ng hnh thnh t t hp li sng Stress th trng, ch khng phi t mt yu t n l.
